ge;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">2020年是結束共產黨在中國的最後一年，否則文貴就從那18樓跳下去，</span></strong></span>大家要記住我的承諾」。"},{"pid":"ebef34fb6739b7a128ae265adc89b0ade1432b98","tid":1501104,"uid":142735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T09:56:31.000Z","msg":"幾時爆習家族D料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}